I"°<h2 id="php">PHP</h2>
<p>Add this line to <code class="highlighter-rouge">php.ini</code>:</p>
<div class="highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>sendmail_path = "/usr/sbin/ssmtp -t"
</code></pre></div></div>

<h2 id="ssmtp">SSMTP</h2>
<ol>
  <li>Edit <code class="highlighter-rouge">/etc/ssmt/ssmtp.conf</code>:
    <div class="highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>root=&lt;$SENDER_ADDRESS&gt;
RewriteDomain=&lt;$SENDER_DOMAIN&gt;
mailhub=&lt;$SMTP_SERVER&gt;:587
AuthUser=&lt;$SMTP_USER&gt;
AuthPass=&lt;$SMTP_PASSWORD&gt;
FromLineOverride=Yes
UseTLS=Yes
UseSTARTTLS=Yes
</code></pre></div>    </div>
  </li>
  <li>Edit <code class="highlighter-rouge">config/ssmtp/revaliases</code>:
    <div class="highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>root:&lt;$SENDER_ADDRESS&gt;:&lt;$SMTP_SERVER&gt;:587
</code></pre></div>    </div>
  </li>
</ol>

